Speaker AI Project With Open AI
First we need to install openai in your pycharm project through:
•	Pip install openai
Then go to the openai website and then open API User keys generate your secret API Key
and the paste it to the openai.key parser. 
The link of OpenAI API Keys is given below:
•	https://platform.openai.com/account/api-keys

 
Then go to OpenAI Models Link that is given below:
•	https://platform.openai.com/docs/models/gpt-4
Select one of the models and then paste it to the model variable in python file.
 
After Selecting your model go to that link completions OpenAI:
•	https://platform.openai.com/docs/api-reference/completions/create
Then copy the format of that model and paste it to the python file and make changes to Complete the completion criteria.
 
For checking your response create a variable and at index 0 print your response. Run the code in terminal and enter any question. 
Now for voice we add speechRecognition and other audio modules in our project we will install
•	Pip install SpeechRecognition
•	Pip install pyaudio
•	Pip install pyttsx3
